# Falcons Cricket Club — Project Description

## Overview

This is the official website for **Falcons Cricket Club**, a recreational cricket team of working professionals (mid-30s to 40s) based in a metropolitan city. The site serves as their public-facing identity — showcasing the squad, match results, gallery, sponsors, and a way to get in touch.

**Tagline:** "Play with Pride. Fly as One."

The site is a single-page application with smooth scroll navigation across sections.

## Tech Stack

| Layer         | Technology                                                     |
|---------------|----------------------------------------------------------------|
| Framework     | React 18 + TypeScript                                          |
| Build Tool    | Vite 5 (SWC plugin)                                            |
| Styling       | Tailwind CSS 3 with custom theme + CSS variables               |
| UI Components | shadcn/ui (Radix primitives, `@/components/ui/`)               |
| Animations    | Framer Motion                                                  |
| Routing       | React Router DOM v6 (single route `/` + 404 catch-all)         |
| State/Data    | TanStack React Query (client configured, no remote data yet)   |
| Charts        | Recharts (available, not actively used yet)                     |
| Forms         | React Hook Form + Zod                                          |
| Testing       | Vitest + React Testing Library + jsdom                         |
| Deployment    | GitHub Pages via GitHub Actions (on push to `main`)            |
| Fonts         | Google Fonts — Oswald (headings), Source Sans 3 (body)         |

